def find_rank(S: str) -> int:
    n = len(S)
    inp = []
    fact = 2
    for i in range(n):
        inp.append(S[i])
        fact *= i + 1
    fact = fact // n
    i = 0
    k = 1
    inp = sorted(inp)
    for element in S:
        block = inp.index(element)
        k += block * fact
        inp.pop(block)
        if i != n - 1:
            fact = fact // (n - i - 1)
        i += 1
    return k
